Hollis Avenue, west side, south of Jamaica Avenue, showing the old Hollis District Schoolhouse No. 2, from 1860 to 1890. Henry Miller's bicycle repair shop was here in the 192O's
and early '30's.
Views 1,2:  Eugene L. Armbruster Collection View 1: 1923
MAY BE REPRODUCED  View 2: 1925
View 3: P. L. Sperr  March 25, 1932
